    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows in every little detail. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
