    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-level condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been performed, including a complete VANOS overhaul and professional rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The factory-spec suspension maintains its original geometry, and the M-variable differential lock provides optimal power delivery. The exterior retains its original depth and luster, while the interior shows no leather bolster compression or pixel degradation in the instrumentation. A mechanically superior example for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
