      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained since day one. This car is in pristine condition, boasting a flawless factory finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Always garage-kept and strictly non-smoking, the interior retains its original fresh scent, with the premium leather upholstery showing zero signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, it is perfect; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete paper trail included. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards. It comes complete with both original keys, all manuals, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
